:"italic_en","text":"an action that a man commits requiring punishment or retaliation to be inflicted upon him in the present world and in the world to come:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any forbidden injurious action:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kull p. 134:) and in the language of the lawyers, especially"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a wounding:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an amputation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a maiming:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janiy~apN","text_ar":"جَنِيَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jinaAyapN","text_ar":"جِنَايَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Ham p. 241:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jnAyp","text_ar":"جناية"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jinaAyaAtN","text_ar":"جِنَايَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janaAyaA","text_ar":"جَنَايَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but the latter of these pls. is of rare occurrence. (Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["Mgh","Msb","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}